  Locus:
    Page: 86
    Verse: 2
Tags:
  - Death
---
Death is the final stage of growth in this life. There is no total death.
Only the body dies. The self or the spirit, or whatever you may wish to
label it, is eternal. You may interpret this in any way that makes you
comfortable.
